Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.05,0:00:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'd known it would end up like this…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.47,0:00:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I never would've taken the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.15,0:00:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't like it from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.33,0:00:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be okay. Just take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.29,0:00:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that bad.\NWe'll be at the hospital soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.96,0:00:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, no hospitals.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.63,0:00:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Get me to the doctor, not the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.97,0:00:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He's at Hellblau Hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.55,0:00:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, I know what you're thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.52,0:00:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If you go to the hospital, the cops\Nwill come and you'll go to prison again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.10,0:01:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But we ain't got time to take you\Nto that underground doc!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.32,0:01:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hellblau… Hotel!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.53,0:01:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Life's more important than prison! If--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.53,0:01:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Take me there now! Hellblau Hotel!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.42,0:01:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you. There's always trouble\Nwhen a woman's involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.96,0:01:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm begging you… Get me to Dr. Tenma fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.56,0:03:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you're not rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.85,0:03:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The man you're about to meet
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.40,0:03:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't a person someone like you\Ncan normally meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.86,0:03:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I should've brought\Nmy autograph book for him to sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.95,0:03:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Screw around and I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.54,0:03:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.72,0:03:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my man, Martin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.05,0:03:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You can leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.60,0:03:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.01,0:03:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to speak with him privately.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.81,0:03:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.11,0:03:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If you screw things up,\NI really will kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.29,0:04:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I sit here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.00,0:04:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.14,0:04:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How many years have you been\Nworking for The Baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.56,0:04:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it's been three years now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.19,0:04:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And before that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.20,0:04:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Prison, huh? How many years?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.78,0:04:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Eight years.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.95,0:04:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,-For murder?\N-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.20,0:04:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You got out pretty quick for murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.21,0:04:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a model inmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.71,0:04:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear you're a model employee too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.17,0:04:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do anything, whatever the job is.\NHowever…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.47,0:05:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,"However"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.30,0:05:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like jobs that involve women.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.76,0:05:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.68,0:05:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't say no to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.43,0:05:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But I just don't like\Ngetting involved with women.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.56,0:05:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This involves a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.02,0:05:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to look after\Na certain woman for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.41,0:05:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What a lousy job.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.53,0:05:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to go to Düsseldorf\Nand bring a certain woman here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.25,0:05:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you don't like\Ngetting involved with women,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.46,0:05:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,you're perfect for this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.26,0:05:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you'll treat this job\Nin a business-like fashion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.48,0:05:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva Heinemann?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.40,0:05:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.02,0:06:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Martin. But my name doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.86,0:06:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I was told to bring you to Frankfurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.91,0:06:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,By whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.91,0:06:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A man wearing glasses\Nand a high-class suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.66,0:06:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A man wearing glasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.29,0:06:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not one of Roberto's men, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.75,0:06:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.25,0:06:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But he's a big shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.71,0:06:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't force you if you don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.05,0:06:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not too thrilled about this either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.47,0:06:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone is after me right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.10,0:06:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.02,0:06:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be my bodyguard?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.44,0:06:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that is part of this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.61,0:06:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.03,0:06:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Carry this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.53,0:06:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go. This is better\Nthan getting killed by that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.21,0:06:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pain in the ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.79,0:07:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The way she swings her hips\Nand the smell of her perfume…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.51,0:07:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's ticking me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.55,0:07:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What a lousy job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.98,0:07:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.85,0:07:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you'd like,\NI can talk about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.19,0:07:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.57,0:07:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's not talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.83,0:07:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Any liquor?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.95,0:07:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have any liquor?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.91,0:07:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I don't drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.08,0:07:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll check out the dining car.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.36,0:08:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right?\NYou're traveling on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.11,0:08:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I happen to be traveling alone too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.87,0:08:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, why don't you tell me\Nwhere you'll be staying?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.45,0:08:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's my business--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.50,0:08:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.84,0:08:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Me? She asked me for a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.42,0:08:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lay a hand on this woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.46,0:09:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you eat in silence?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.51,0:09:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said before, I'll talk if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.09,0:09:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you drink liquor?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.06,0:09:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,My mom was a horrible alcoholic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.02,0:09:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can drink if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.98,0:09:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet your mom had\Na good reason for drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.90,0:09:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.53,0:09:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I sure do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.74,0:09:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, I have\Na very good reason for my drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.87,0:09:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead. Please tell me.\NIf you hate eating in silence, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.12,0:09:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a long story.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.58,0:09:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine. Tell it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.67,0:09:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I once had a fiancé.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.76,0:09:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a Japanese surgeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.22,0:10:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He was an extremely gifted surgeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.36,0:10:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And then…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.32,0:10:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I tried\Nto shoot and kill my ex-fiancé.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.70,0:10:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that surprise you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.00,0:10:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to kill that guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.00,0:10:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But you didn't shoot him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.13,0:10:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Compared to my story, that's a lot better.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.59,0:10:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your story?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.80,0:10:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.22,0:10:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I shot them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.23,0:10:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,My woman, who was screwing\Nanother man in our bedroom,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.56,0:10:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and the man as well.\NI shot them until I ran out of bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.40,0:10:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The room was filled\Nwith the smell of her blood,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.86,0:10:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,the smell of his blood\Nand, the smell of perfume.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.78,0:11:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,When I came to my senses,\NI was standing there by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.25,0:11:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure are an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.79,0:11:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.26,0:12:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What a lousy job.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.49,0:12:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,My employer is waiting inside this hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.74,0:12:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a murderer, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.49,0:12:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't touch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.41,0:12:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What room?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.71,0:12:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.33,0:12:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not dressed appropriately\Nto enter this hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You can wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.51,0:12:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Room 1014.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.65,0:12:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.45,0:13:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what the man in glasses\Nwants from that woman,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.79,0:13:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,but if she turns him down,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.08,0:13:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,this lousy job will be over\Nand I won't have to see that woman again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.43,0:13:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?\NYou're looking a little pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.31,0:13:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It was an acceptable deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.65,0:13:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I can use this card all I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.53,0:13:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you waiting for? We're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.45,0:13:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Going where?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.70,0:13:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.42,0:13:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a lousy job.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.30,0:14:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the next place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.84,0:14:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a men's clothing store.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.88,0:14:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I need you to wear something proper.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.22,0:14:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.31,0:14:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.31,0:14:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't have the man I'm with\Ndressed like a bum.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.60,0:14:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.02,0:14:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And a necktie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.28,0:15:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenzo…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.79,0:15:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Try these on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.96,0:15:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A necktie, huh? This blows.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.51,0:15:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-How is it?\N-Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.43,0:15:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice. You're looking better.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.02,0:15:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But fix that necktie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.03,0:15:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit swaggering your shoulders\Nlike some mobster when you walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.24,0:15:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just walking normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.62,0:15:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Normal for you isn't normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.37,0:15:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, you need to protect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.08,0:16:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter where we go,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.59,0:16:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I need you to act in a way\Nthat won't disgrace me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.18,0:16:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's your job, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.89,0:16:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. That is my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.23,0:16:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Get your elbows off the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.10,0:16:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Use your fork with your left\Nand your knife with your right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.78,0:16:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make noise when you eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.62,0:16:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I guess it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.12,0:16:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.66,0:16:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Your story.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.66,0:16:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,About you being the classy daughter\Nof a hospital director.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.58,0:16:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You thought I was lying?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.46,0:16:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Until I brought you to this city,\Nyou looked like just some alcoholic woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.42,0:16:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What about now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.67,0:16:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a classy woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.22,0:16:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my true form.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.47,0:16:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva Heinemann has returned\Nto where she belongs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.52,0:17:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.02,0:17:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A party invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.61,0:17:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,-A party?\N-That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.57,0:17:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the job I was given.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.99,0:17:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A job?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.53,0:17:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm supposed to attend several parties.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.41,0:17:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.37,0:17:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be glad.\NThat sounds like a fun job.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.37,0:17:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You're coming with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.33,0:17:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll play the part of a man\Nwho's worthy of escorting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.80,0:17:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This job's just getting lousier.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.45,0:18:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,How does it feel\Nfinally being back on your home turf?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.77,0:18:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What could be so damn funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.36,0:18:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell do these people here\Ntalk about anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.74,0:18:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,About the weather? What about stocks?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.07,0:18:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even know\Nwhat language they're speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.63,0:18:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This is making me nauseous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.59,0:18:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So, there you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.64,0:19:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind me. You have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.43,0:19:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,-We're going.\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.60,0:19:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We're leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.60,0:19:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.11,0:19:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He wasn't at this party.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.23,0:19:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,My job is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.69,0:19:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's not here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.11,0:19:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Take me away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.74,0:19:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Take me anywhere.\NJust get me out of here fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.83,0:19:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Her hand was trembling…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.00,0:19:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,but I didn't know why at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.81,0:19:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I survived the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.06,0:19:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.81,0:19:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you'd returned\Nto where you belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.74,0:19:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to live\Nthat kind of life every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.78,0:20:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought if I returned to that world\Nthat my true self would return.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.16,0:20:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But now, a bar like this is\Nthe only place you feel at home, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.42,0:20:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't where I belong either!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.88,0:20:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Not here! Not there either!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.09,0:20:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no place where I belong!\NI already knew that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.35,0:20:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, when this job is over,\NI'm sure I'll be murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.49,0:20:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it would be better\Nthan being killed by Roberto in Düsseldorf
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.32,0:20:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,where I was a total mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.83,0:20:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it would be better to be killed\Nas the beautiful Eva Heinemann.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.71,0:20:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But when you die…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.30,0:20:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,it's all the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.98,0:21:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to protect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.65,0:21:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a bad habit of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.19,0:21:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of the blue,\NI suddenly wanted to protect this woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.56,0:21:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Christ!\NHow the hell did this happen anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.36,0:21:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why… we're going to Dr. Tenma…\Nso I can tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.99,0:22:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there!\NJust a little longer! We're almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.75,0:22:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A necktie…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.75,0:22:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If it hadn't been for this…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.25,0:22:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I never would've been there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.30,0:22:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I never would've seen…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.18,0:22:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,such terror.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.56,0:23:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Subtitle translation by: Brian Athey
